", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說你睡覺認床，離開諾伯特區立馬失眠！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許當時我應該努力克服一下。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉倒吧！你什麼人我還不知道？你要是睡不著，大家就都別想安生！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可不想再在睏得要死的時候被你拉著聊天了！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈哈，這些日子，我倒是在哪都睡得著。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#5$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，太累了嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許吧。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#5$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是發現......睡覺是放空大腦的最好方法。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#8$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......等到羅德島的任務結束，貝爾德，我會帶你們離開這裡。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶你們所有人一起。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來來來，讓我們開瓶酒慶祝一下這個時隔幾年的重逢吧！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然都是些便宜貨，但放了那麼久，說不定就變好喝了呢？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根，給貝爾德看看你寫的那些書！說說我們一路的冒險！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，貝爾德，你可是錯過了成為國王歷險記裡一員的機會——", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......摩根？你怎麼了？你好像一直臉色都不是很好。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可是好不容易回家了！你應該高興一點。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想......我踩到的那隻......手。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能只是個意外。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那隻手上有一枚扳指，我總覺得我在哪裡見過。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應當記得......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可就是怎麼都想不起來。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......貝爾德，諾伯特區這些天發生了什麼？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒什麼，摩根，或許真的只是場意外。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都在努力地活下去，僅此而已。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些都過去了，你們回來了，我們很快就會離開這裡，這就夠了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾伯特區，這裡是我們的家。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想過我們回來時候的樣子，我還以為第一夜我們會去那家撞球廳玩個通宵，再去隔壁那家酒吧喝個天昏地暗。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者找影廳的麥克拉倫包場，看十場連續放映的冒險電影。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了，但我不敢仔細看。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些碎掉的玻璃和玻璃上乾涸的血，那些倒在裡面的......黑影。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該像我一樣，好好睡一覺。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一路過來，你們都太累了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，你現在有那把國劍了，你會是那個英雄，對吧？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會救下諾伯特區的，我們會救下諾伯特區的。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些都只是暫時的艱難罷了，對吧！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當然。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會奪回過去的生活的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許......", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#8$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，已經很晚了，休息吧，夥計們。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天還有一大堆事情要忙。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德說的對，摩根，我們都需要......好好休息一下。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g2_glasgowoldroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王蜷縮在沙發上，她曾經在這裡度過無數個夜晚，這裡的每一寸觸感她仍然熟悉。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還記得很多年前，她們在舊貨市場上淘到了這張老沙發，四個人花了吃奶的力氣才把這破東西搬上拳館的二樓。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那時，這座沙發對於她還稱得上是寬廣，很快，她就得把腳翹在扶手上才能在這裡容身。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在黑暗中，推進之王的手撫過沙發的每一寸。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是漢娜練習耍她那把小刀時留下的劃痕，她當時為此內疚了三天。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根曾把一大瓶飲料灑在這裡，她買了罐劣質清潔劑來處理污漬，最後越弄越糟，至今都留有大片滑膩的痕跡。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德把熨斗放在沙發上忘了關，差點燒著了整個房間。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i03", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她曾以為這樣的日子永遠不會變。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她曾堅信這樣的日子永遠不會變。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是她們的格拉斯哥幫，她們的街區，她們成長的地方，她們的家。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 3.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 3.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.8, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，她回來了。"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可她的心中，卻沒有一絲欣喜。"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她又想起了摩根的那本“回憶錄”，《偉大的維娜陛下和她偉大的朋友們》。"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王輕輕觸碰著放在身邊的諸王之息。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那把劍依然冰冷如初。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領袖。英雄。國王。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王維娜。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞歷山德莉娜·維娜·維多利亞。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，維娜？", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這件衣服太重了，睡覺時壓得我喘不過氣。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想找幾件更舒服的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那個抽屜裡。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chairrub", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armour", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你這些年沒長個，嗯？", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們都多大了，早過了長個子的年紀。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成長這東西可說不準，我記得我們第一次遇見的時候，你明明才那麼高......", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了行了，又是你那套感歎時間流逝的老話。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些老話，我可是很多年沒有可以講的對象了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......抱歉，貝爾德。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回來就好，維娜陛下。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別這麼叫我。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就還是叫你，推進之王。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g10_wildbattlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，埃芒加德女士？", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別叫我女士，我還沒那麼老。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，埃芒加德......小姐？我搞不太清你們巫妖的年紀......", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，算了，就叫我埃芒加德女士吧。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這艘高速軍艦毀得還真徹底，嘖，血魔的人還又把這裡洗了一遍。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德將軍說，這會是薩卡茲勝利的開始。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，薩卡茲的勝利。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，那位凱爾希女士一再警告我，這樣的未來無法給我們帶來任何東西。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#11$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我還是不明白，我的老師為什麼會有一位菲林老朋友？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#11$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，我討厭這裡的味道。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請跟我來，特蕾西婭殿下在等您。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g1_glasgowboxinggym", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，早安。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#16$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需要對接下來的行動......做出安排了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲把這些平民當做他們不被炮火直接襲擊的保險，但無論是軍事委員會還是大公爵，我們都不能真的相信他們的仁慈。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算我們無視這些正發生在他們之間的博弈，現在封鎖區的糟糕狀況，我們也都看在眼裡。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們已經看到了如今諾伯特區的混亂情況，要改變現狀並不容易。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們帶來的那些藥物......我清點過數量，恐怕只是杯水車薪。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，僅僅憑藉我們，能做到的事情實在有限，但這不是我們裹足不前的理由。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "針對飛空艇的調查和對地塊平民的撤離計劃必須同時展開，我們不能忽視任何一邊。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，戴菲恩小姐？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們很厲害，對吧？你們能穿過薩卡茲的封鎖來到這裡，你們應該同樣能輕鬆抽身而出。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以驕傲地說，現在聚集在這裡的都是羅德島了不起的幹員，但是很抱歉，戴菲恩小姐，我們恐怕沒有你想像的那麼強大。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比於那些戰爭背後的操縱者，我們甚至稱得上十足弱小。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以......你們是接受了幫助才能進來這裡？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按那位先生一直強調的說法，恐怕該說成是“交易”，而且很不光彩。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是......薩卡茲？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "某位大公爵居然與另一批薩卡茲達成了合作......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，看來你琢磨的東西很多。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，我只是經常讀報罷了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是個好習慣。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們正在策劃一場撤離行動，是嗎？你們背後的那位大人物承諾了幫忙？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，沒有，她看起來並不在乎。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是你們顯然很在乎。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，這些人可是羅德島。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#4$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對此不發表意見，我更關心我們能不能活著離開這裡。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#4$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一個提議，羅德島的各位，這可能有點冒險......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲封鎖了所有諾伯特區向外傳遞消息的管道，我能猜到他們對外的說辭。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信，無論是哪個大公爵，都很清楚那不過是“說辭”而已。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們不會主動戳破，不如說，大公爵和卡茲戴爾軍事委員會反倒在這一點上達成了默契。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲把這地塊上的人當盾牌，大公爵們何嘗不是？我猜，要是這裡的人被薩卡茲殺了個一乾二淨，有幾位大公爵反倒會長舒一口氣。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一場戰爭中，某些人只會把道德視作負擔。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，您說的沒錯。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們......就打破這種默契。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們必須推一把大公爵們，逼迫他們更果斷地行動起來。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......在我們真的全都死在這裡之前。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好幾天了，戈爾丁，你總是一言不發。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就我們所知，你不是個如此沉默的人。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍的情況怎麼樣了？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們離開了這座城市。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還剩下多少人？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許不多。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，又是沉默。沉默能給你帶來安寧嗎？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是在......回憶他們，回憶他們每一個人。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，好啦，戈爾丁，你並不天然地屬於他們，你自然也可以忘卻這一種虛無的歸屬。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並不是你親手殺了他們，大部分人本就會死在這場戰爭裡。你們甚至為此發明了一個詞，“犧牲”。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些名字，那些藏匿於名字之後的人，大部分你甚至都從未見過。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成為一個集體的一員能讓你感到快樂和驕傲嗎？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，如你所見，我們只能歸屬於我們自己。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我曾以為是......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一開始，我以為我為之奮鬥的是我們共同的夢想，是自救軍的事業。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾天我發現，或許並非如此。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托說的話是對的，我們都是一類人。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾說他悲觀......我又何嘗不是呢。不管我自己承不承認......我都是一個容易失望的人。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自救軍的成員們或許是懷著純潔的理念而奮鬥的人，但是自救軍本身不是。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是克洛維希婭還是阿勒黛......我尊重她們的為人，可是她們的目的絕不僅僅像是嘴上說的那樣。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在很長一段時間裡，假裝自己對這些毫無察覺。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在為此感到幻滅了。你終於察覺到你的事業從一開始就並非純潔無瑕。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得你的努力都是徒勞。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我不去想什麼事業，我只是在想那些人。那一張張的面孔。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海蒂、費斯特、洛洛、老比爾、亞當斯、小喬治......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有資格，也沒有權利自稱我該為倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍悔罪。我不需屬於那些虛幻的集體。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我需要......在心中面對他們每一個人。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}